### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5050/api/health

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:5050/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

### Create User
POST http://localhost:5050/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5050/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User by ID (with auth token)
GET http://localhost:5050/api/users/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Update User
PUT http://localhost:5050/api/users/123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "John Updated"
}

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:5050/api/users/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE